{"tid":2293331,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺幾年後普通話會取代英文，成為國際語言","createTime":"2020-11-20T07:20:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T08:27:06.000Z","uid":226231,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c557b8d5b443be86d6db9f46c5ba5639e5f01900","tid":2293331,"uid":226231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:20:57.000Z","msg":"唔好話我唔提你地，依家快啲學好普通話未來大把前途"},{"pid":"153bade6a956ccc62aa81bf7894a89715c9c85b2","tid":2293331,"uid":226231,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:21:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91e81776395a296080f2362e83ed86e26570fe7","tid":2293331,"uid":49136,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:22:50.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係 又何來取代？"},{"pid":"fb34a01e2e71c083efce04ab5ea8712f062a1918","tid":2293331,"uid":226231,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b91e81776395a296080f2362e83ed86e26570fe7","tid":2293331,"uid":49136,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:22:50.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係 又何來取代？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:24:31.000Z","msg":"細個冇學好普通話，大個咗先嚟後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a83a0f1de05244981e5befc572daf192716ea9c","tid":2293331,"uid":268516,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:52:38.000Z","msg":"你媽死了"},{"pid":"dcce40300c8aa5663692e9c7777ab64667a83472","tid":2293331,"uid":45745,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:53:24.000Z","msg":"nmsl"},{"pid":"7663a89d4926f50f957e43ff18d757328ad885d3","tid":2293331,"uid":24570,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:56:03.000Z","msg":"仲要学埋简体，简直牛b"},{"pid":"043c8593ea5809139487293b1f74648651121c04","tid":2293331,"uid":226231,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7663a89d4926f50f957e43ff18d757328ad885d3","tid":2293331,"uid":24570,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:56:03.000Z","msg":"仲要学埋简体，简直牛b"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:56:21.000Z","msg":"対<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4569d7acd10c9416c1077c9f9ab592dae7372427","tid":2293331,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T08:09:58.000Z","msg":"起華爾街飲茅台，有個鬼妹想溝我<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2272379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2272379</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n身爲黃皮膚的我，走在華爾街，洋鬼子都對我彬彬有禮。<br />\n<br />\n走進餐廳，用洋文問我吃什麼。我用國語回答：你說啥？<br />\n<br />\n洋鬼子連忙道歉，換了個懂國語的人出來。<br />\n<br />\n吃飽後喝著茅台，旁邊的洋鬼妞看者我垂涎三尺。她走過來，想跟我共醉，問我晚上有沒有空。我二話不說，拖著洋鬼妞的手，去了酒店。<br />\n<br />\n2小時後，我打算離開，洋鬼妞纏著我，說想嫁給我，因為她想移民中國。<br />\n<br />\n那一刻，我心中的紅太陽緩緩升起，頸上的紅領巾隨風飄擺。<br />\n<br />\n那一刻，我知道，社會主義好，我是社會社會主義的接班人！"},{"pid":"9cafbc68e4075ebacafc10ef9691f141d3fe2515","tid":2293331,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T08:27:06.000Z","msg":"過到文字呢關先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中文字又難寫，讀音又冇章法<br />\n叫啲鬼佬點記"}]}